      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "You can describe the neighborhood as a dimly lit, rundown area with crumbling buildings, overgrown lots, and trash-filled streets. The air is thick with the smell of decay and desperation, and the only sound is the distant hum of sirens and the occasional shout or scuffle. The residents, mostly Black and Latino, keep to themselves, their windows boarded up and their doors locked tight, as if afraid of what might happen if they venture out after dark. The streets are narrow and winding, making it easy to get lost, and the shadows seem to writhe and twist on the walls like living things.",
